  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN OUR DISCORD</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>ROCK, PLAY and PERFORM! <br>A unique VR game to live the ultimate ROCKSTAR experience!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/547670/extras/ae4abeaffde77aa86e553eb699650ff7.webp?t=1712084829\" width=616 height=35 /></span><br>Step in to your favorite stage to unleash your inner ROCKSTAR and electrify your audience with your powerful sound. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/547670/extras/1244278dd25d6797e7e739e5842d0287.poster.avif?t=1712084829\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/547670/extras/1244278dd25d6797e7e739e5842d0287.webm?t=1712084829\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/547670/extras/1244278dd25d6797e7e739e5842d0287.mp4?t=1712084829\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/547670/extras/def06ccecf0900f9d4bd6a40c150c976.webp?t=1712084829\" width=616 height=35 /></span><br>Play music by shooting, punching and moving notes. Experience the rush of performing in front of a roaring audience as you hit all the right notes. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/547670/extras/0a5f2b5fb6d6a2e37962197aeb44d336.poster.avif?t=1712084829\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/547670/extras/0a5f2b5fb6d6a2e37962197aeb44d336.webm?t=1712084829\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/547670/extras/0a5f2b5fb6d6a2e37962197aeb44d336.mp4?t=1712084829\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/547670/extras/339308226360c169654bfd35ecfe4c97.webp?t=1712084829\" width=616 height=35 /></span><br>Musical Range transports you to five unique stages, each with its own atmosphere and stunning visuals that will leave you breathless. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/547670/extras/6d7d732c4ac09073eee9e6200f0be02b.poster.avif?t=1712084829\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/547670/extras/6d7d732c4ac09073eee9e6200f0be02b.webm?t=1712084829\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/547670/extras/6d7d732c4ac09073eee9e6200f0be02b.mp4?t=1712084829\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/547670/extras/0538842d8570eb0fb46da6a0d78f502d.webp?t=1712084829\" width=616 height=35 /></span><br>Grab your guns, feel the music and try the 4 different instrument sounds that we designed for you. Mix and match as many times as you want while you are playing a song or let the game guide you with the automatic tone system.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/547670/extras/d528d36d6d31ab1db80348eb2d22e3f4.poster.avif?t=1712084829\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/547670/extras/d528d36d6d31ab1db80348eb2d22e3f4.webm?t=1712084829\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/547670/extras/d528d36d6d31ab1db80348eb2d22e3f4.mp4?t=1712084829\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/547670/extras/3f5ae95d9a475a9564d2924f36a7e2b7.webp?t=1712084829\" width=616 height=35 /></span><br>Enjoy Musical Range with your own music. Expand your private music library with new songs and have fun.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/547670/extras/41a95509d0e41e941cc4202a7080381c.poster.avif?t=1712084829\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/547670/extras/41a95509d0e41e941cc4202a7080381c.webm?t=1712084829\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/547670/extras/41a95509d0e41e941cc4202a7080381c.mp4?t=1712084829\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Are you ready to ROCK the world with Musical Range? Grab your headset, feel the music and become a ROCKSTAR!",
